# Title: VMMap Unsigned Dbghelp.DLL Potential Sideloading
# Author: Nasreddine Bencherchali (Nextron Systems)
# Date: 2023-07-28
# Level: high
# Description: Detects potential DLL sideloading of an unsigned dbghelp.dll by the Sysinternals VMMap.
# MITRE Tactic: Defense Evasion
# Tags: attack.defense-evasion, attack.persistence, attack.privilege-escalation, attack.t1574.001
# Reference: https://github.com/SigmaHQ/sigma/blob/master/rules/windows/image_load/image_load_side_load_vmmap_dbghelp_unsigned.yml

ImageLoaded="*C:\\Debuggers\\dbghelp.dll*" Image IN ("*\\vmmap.exe", "*\\vmmap64.exe") NOT Signed="true"